snippet.title: Around the World in 80 Days Teaser Trailer - Walkabout Mini Golf
snippet.description:
For the final installment in our Jules Verne trilogy, Around the World in 80 Days will have you putting through stanchions, ramps, pneumatic tubes, hot air balloons, and all of the decadent luxuries of Port Eiffel as you board your airship... this Thursday!

#vr #vrgaming #walkaboutminigolf #psvr2 #metaquest #steam
